    <div class="about">
    <h1>About Us</h1>
    <p> Hello listeners! Thank Your for listening to The Grand Bruno Hall Podcast.<br> The purpose of this podcast is 
        to explore the different lives of students<br> 
        and staff at Birmingham-Southern College. If you know BSC you know<br>
        about E-Term! So in the month of January in 2023 Co-Host Bella Ayala and<br>
        Nicole Villavicencio-Garduño along with Producer Mallie Taylor set out to <br>
        reach a goal of creating eight audio and video episodes with different topics<br>
        and guest. In addition, building a website using Html and CSS to access each<br>
        episode on the website and linking other listening platforms like Spotify and<br>
        YouTube. We are excited to be able to have an opprotunity to create a project<br>
        about the amazing school we attend.
    </p>
    </div>
  
 
